project_descr: Coordinated National Response to HIV/AIDS &-Tuberculosis in War-torn and Highly Stigmatized Settings

outputs.output_descr: Improved prevention of the spread of HIV and increased survival rates of people living with HIV/AIDS, including strengthened national capacity to manage Global Fund grants (Scaling up Universal Access for Most at Risk Populations in BIH).
donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS

outputs.output_descr: Increase survival rates of people living with HIV/AIDS one year after diagnosis from 25% to 90% by establishing VCT (Voluntary counseling and testing) services and referral system and Decreasing stigma and discrimination.
donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS
